               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18690111-name-428" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18690111-name-428" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18690111-name-428" type="surname" value="RAMSEY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18690111-name-428" type="given" value="ROBERT"></interp>ROBERT RAMSEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I live at 36, Beech Street—about 1.10 or 1.15, I was in Beech Street, going in the direction of Chiswell Street—I saw the prisoner running, and the prosecutor following—my dog called my attention to it—I saw the prisoner stopped by two persons—I called out "Police!" and he was given into custody.</p>
               <p>
